"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwangdoc=self.webpackChunkwangdoc||[]).push([[9884],{28091:(n,e,a)=>{a.r(e),a.d(e,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-13459472",path:"/git-tutorial/commands/git-branch.html",title:"git branch",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{summary:"git branch git branch是分支操作命令。 （1）新建一个分支 直接在git branch后面跟上分支名，就表示新建该分支。 新建一个分支，指向当前 commit。本质是在refs/heads/目录中生成一个文件，文件名为分支名，内容为当前 commit 的哈希值。 注意，创建后，还是停留在原来分支，需要用git checkout切换到新建分",head:[["meta",{property:"og:url",content:"https://yzqbooks.github.io/wangdoc/wangdoc/git-tutorial/commands/git-branch.html"}],["meta",{property:"og:site_name",content:"wangdoc"}],["meta",{property:"og:title",content:"git branch"}],["meta",{property:"og:type",content:"article"}],["meta",{property:"og:updated_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}],["meta",{property:"og:locale",content:"zh-CN"}],["meta",{property:"article:modified_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}]]},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"命令行参数",slug:"命令行参数",children:[{level:3,title:"-d",slug:"d",children:[]}]}],git:{createdTime:164923974e4,updatedTime:164923974e4,contributors:[{name:"yzqdev",email:"yzqdev@outlook.com",commits:1}]},readingTime:{minutes:1.17,words:352},filePathRelative:"git-tutorial/commands/git-branch.md"}},30151:(n,e,a)=>{a.r(e),a.d(e,{default:()=>t});const s=(0,a(66252).uE)('<h1 id="git-branch" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#git-branch" aria-hidden="true">#</a> git branch</h1><p><code>git branch</code>是分支操作命令。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 列出所有本地分支</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch\n\n<span class="token comment"># 列出所有本地分支和远程分支</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -a\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><p>（1）新建一个分支</p><p>直接在<code>git branch</code>后面跟上分支名，就表示新建该分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch develop\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>新建一个分支，指向当前 commit。本质是在<code>refs/heads/</code>目录中生成一个文件，文件名为分支名，内容为当前 commit 的哈希值。</p><p>注意，创建后，还是停留在原来分支，需要用<code>git checkout</code>切换到新建分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> checkout develop\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>使用<code>-b</code>参数，可以新建的同时，切换到新分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> checkout -b NewBranch MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>（2）删除分支</p><p><code>-d</code>参数用来删除一个分支，前提是该分支没有未合并的变动。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -d <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>分支名<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>强制删除一个分支，不管有没有未合并变化。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -D <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>分支名<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>（3）分支改名</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> checkout -b twitter-experiment feature132\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -d feature132\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p>另一种写法</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 为当前分支改名</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -m twitter-experiment\n\n<span class="token comment"># 为指定分支改名</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -m feature132 twitter-experiment\n\n<span class="token comment"># 如果有重名分支，强制改名</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -m feature132 twitter-experiment\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br></div></div><p>（4）查看 merge 情况</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># Shows branches that are all merged in to your current branch</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch --merged\n\n<span class="token comment"># Shows branches that are not merged in to your current branch</span>\n$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch --no-merged\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><h2 id="命令行参数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#命令行参数" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 命令行参数</h2><h3 id="d" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#d" aria-hidden="true">#</a> -d</h3><p><code>-d</code>参数用于删除一个指定分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -d <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>branchname<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div>',26),r={},t=(0,a(83744).Z)(r,[["render",function(n,e){return s}]])},83744:(n,e)=>{e.Z=(n,e)=>{const a=n.__vccOpts||n;for(const[n,s]of e)a[n]=s;return a}}}]);